QuestData.Title: The Zandalari Prophecy
QuestData.Description: Dear $p,$b$bI have read your reports on the Zandalari and believe I have some clues as to their most recent aggression.$b$bIf you visit us at the Seat of Knowledge in Vale of Eternal Blossoms we can add this contribution to your personal collection.$b$bThank you for your diligence!$b$bSincerely,$b$bLorewalker Cho
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring The Zandalari Prophecy to Lorewalker Cho.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Lorewalker Cho at the Seat of Knowledge in Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
